## Critical Finding: Targeting Changes
- v65 had a different targeting function: hub_penalty style, expansion*5 cap 30
- Current code has network_penalty*0.5, expansion*10 cap 60, hotspot penalty
- These changes (v133-v137) made targeting WORSE for tournament
- Created AlphaV65ReplicaPolicy: base budgets, no network/hotspot penalties
- v65 replica scores 0.29 at 500 steps vs base's 0.25 — slightly better!

